Description: 
        Cocopot
        ---------
        
        Cocopot is a microframework for Python. Foucus on mobile service and cloud service, no default template system.
        
        Cocopot is Fun
        ```````````````````````
        
        .. code:: python
        
            from cocopot import Cocopot
            app = Cocopot()
        
            @app.route("/")
            def hello():
                return "Hello World!"
        
            if __name__ == "__main__":
                app.run()
        
        And Easy to Setup
        ```````````````````````
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            $ pip install Cocopot
            $ python hello.py
             * Running on http://localhost:3000/
        
        
